h different line number (i.e. `rspec double_run_spec.rb:3 double_run_spec.rb:7`), all specs in that file are run twice. I expect each spec is run only once, the result should be same as `rspec double_run_spec.rb:3:7`\n## How to reproduce? \n\n`double_run_spec.rb`:\n\n``` ruby\n  describe \"Universe\" do\n\n    it \"should support basic math operations\" do\n      (1 + 1).should == 2\n    end\n\n    it \"should have answer to all questions\" do\n      42.should == 42\n    end\n\n  end\n```\n\nCalling\n\n```\n> rspec double_run_spec.rb:3 double_run_spec.rb:7\n```\n\nresults in \n\n```\nRun filtered including {:locations=>{\"./double_run_spec.rb\"=>[3, 7]}}\n....\n\nFinished in 0.21457 seconds\n4 examples, 0 failures\n```\n\nOnly two examples should be run.\n\n(RSpec 2.7.1)\n","closed_by":{"login":"dchelimsky","id":1075,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNzU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1075?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky","html_url":"https://github.com/dchelimsky","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dchelimsky/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/546/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/546/t